-- 
2011-04-03T22:26:05Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-03/minmetals-resources-offers-to-buy-australia-s-equinox-for-6-54-billion.html
Minmetals Resources Ltd. (1208)  will offer
to buy  Equinox Minerals Ltd. (EQN)  for about C$6.3 billion in cash,
according to a statement to the Hong Kong stock exchange.
Minmetals will pay C$7 a share, 23 percent more than the last
closing price, for all the shares in Equinox it doesnâ€™t already
